Text: I'm not positive, but I think this is the promo/bootleg version of The Ring 2 OST. If it is, the quality could possibly be lower. Just a warning.

These soundtracks are from Ringu and Ringu 2, not the new OST for The Ring and The Ring TwO. 
They're still excellent soundtracks, but not the American film OSTs. :)
